OL,3,CSurge in flu patients in intensive
OL,4,Ccare as hospitals face mounting
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FThere are fresh warnings about the
OL,8,Fpressure mounting on England's NHS
OL,9,Fafter another surge in flu cases, as
OL,10,FITV News' Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,11,FBarry reports
OL,13,FHospitals in England have seen a rise
OL,14,Fin the number of patients being
OL,15,Fadmitted to intensive care with flu,
OL,16,Fas NHS leaders warn they are facing
OL,17,Fmounting pressure this winter.
