OL,3,CSurge in flu patients in intensive
OL,4,Ccare as hospitals face mounting
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FNHS figures show the number of people
OL,8,Fin hospital with flu has jumped by 41%
OL,9,Fin a week ` this is four times higher
OL,10,Fthan at the same point last year.
OL,12,FHealth leaders warn the situation
OL,13,Fcould get "worse before it gets
OL,14,Fbetter" as Christmas and festive
OL,15,Fgatherings take place.
OL,17,FIn the intensive care unit at Kings
OL,18,FMill hospital in Nottinghamshire,
OL,19,Fdoctors told ITV News four people have
OL,20,Fbeen admitted after becoming
OL,21,Fcritically ill with the flu.
