OL,3,CSurge in flu patients in intensive
OL,4,Ccare as hospitals face mounting
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FOne patient is a 42-year-old father of
OL,8,Fthree who has been in an induced coma
OL,9,Ffor a week. He was previously fit and
OL,10,Fhealthy.
OL,12,FHis partner, Alex, told ITV News: "It
OL,13,Falmost becomes a new norm where you
OL,14,Ffeel like you're in a dream and you're
OL,15,Fjust functioning because you have to
OL,16,Ffunction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
