OL,7,F"But that's really difficult.
OL,8,FEverybody is hoping and praying for
OL,9,Fhim to make a speedy recovery, and I
OL,10,Fthink we're coming to terms with the
OL,11,Ffact that it's not necessarily going
OL,12,Fto be speedy."
OL,14,FPhaedra Kay, a critical care nurse at
OL,15,FKing's Mill hospital, said the unit is
OL,16,F"exceptionally busy" and every bed was
OL,17,F"filled" on Thursday morning.
