OL,3,CSurge in flu patients in intensive
OL,4,Ccare as hospitals face mounting
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,F"We have proned patients, which means
OL,8,Fturning them onto their tummies to
OL,9,Fventilate them better, which is
OL,10,Fsomething we did a lot during Covid,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,FAs a result of the surge in flu cases,
OL,14,Fthe hospital has reintroduced the
OL,15,Fwearing of face masks.
OL,17,FAccording to the latest NHS data, an
OL,18,Faverage of 2,629 flu patients were in
OL,19,Fbeds in England each day last week,
OL,20,F2,504 in general or acute (G&A) beds
OL,21,Fand 125 in critical care.
