OL,3,CSurge in flu patients in intensive
OL,4,Ccare as hospitals face mounting
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FThis is up 41% from a total of 1,861
OL,8,Fpatients the previous week, when 1,795
OL,9,Fwere in G&A beds and 66 were in
OL,10,Fcritical care.
OL,12,FIt is also more than four times the
OL,13,Ffigure at this stage in 2023, when the
OL,14,Ftotal stood at 648, and higher than
OL,15,Fthe equivalent week in 2022, when the
OL,16,Faverage was 2,088.
OL,18,FNHS England are continuing to urge
OL,19,Fpeople to get their flu jabs as
OL,20,Fleaders say they have been "hit hard
OL,21,Fwith an early festive flu season."
