OL,3,CSurge in flu patients in intensive
OL,4,Ccare as hospitals face mounting
OL,5,Cpressure
OL,7,FProfessor Sir Stephen Powis, NHS
OL,8,Fnational medical director, said: "As
OL,9,Fchildren finish school and friends and
OL,10,Ffamilies congregate over the Christmas
OL,11,Fperiod we expect viruses to continue
OL,12,Fto spread so if you haven't got your
OL,13,Fflu jab and are eligible please come
OL,14,Fforward."
OL,16,FIt comes after officials warned of a
OL,17,Fso-called "quad-demic" of disease;
OL,18,Fflu, Covid-19, respiratory syncytial
OL,19,Fvirus (RSV) and norovirus.
